rows.label: tlk43310148_05_msg0001
rows.name:
Never thought I'd live to see the day
when Invidia and Superbia had to
join forces to survive.

rows.label: tlk43310148_05_msg0002
rows.name:
Till now, Invidia and the Superbians have
only been lookin' out for number one.

rows.label: tlk43310148_05_msg0003
rows.name:
I guess your way of thinking changes
when the fate of the whole of Alst
is at stake though.

rows.label: tlk43310148_05_msg0004
rows.name: But I mean...maybe it's a good thing.
